Really do admire what @ladygaga has done.

If you haven't seen #AStarIsBorn yet go do so.

She is an amazing talent who I was lucky to see live many years ago when I took a young @jadedc to see The Pussycat Dolls where Gaga was the support act! She is the ultimate performer and you can see how hard she works to become the success she now is.

Be fearless with your ambitions!

#quotestoliveby #gaga #gagaquotes #inspirationalquotes

They are League of Origin where the best League of Legends players from @oceanicproleague will take on each other under the banner of Victoria NSW Queensland and NZ being run and promoted by the @afl at @mcourtarena

Why do I care? Well now I'm an #esports team owner joining 7 teams who have been leading the way growing esports in Australia. It is an exciting step I'm looking forward to the challenge and helping the OPL grow on and off the pitch/court/field/map. I clearly don't have all my esports terms down but super excited to what my team can bring.

Full details at SportsGeekHQ.com or head to NewOPLTeam.com.au to join the fun
